OL,3,CMcMonagle employment may have
OL,4,C'resulted in misuse of public money',
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FA former Sinn Fein press officer who
OL,8,Fwas later convicted of sex offences
OL,9,Fmisrepresented details of his
OL,10,Femployment which may have resulted in
OL,11,Fa misuse of public money, a review has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FThe review found that Michael
OL,15,FMcMonagle simultaneously held two full-
OL,16,Ftime jobs working for Sinn Fein
OL,17,Fpoliticians while also working as a
OL,18,Fpress officer for three months in
OL,19,F2020, including being employed by then
OL,20,Fdeputy First Minister Michelle O'Neill.
