OL,3,CMcMonagle employment may have
OL,4,C'resulted in misuse of public money',
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FAssembly Chief Executive Lesley Hogg
OL,8,Fhas told MLAs that the issue has now
OL,9,Fbeen referred to the PSNI.
OL,11,FMs Hogg commissioned the review of
OL,12,FAssembly members' allowances in
OL,13,FOctober in the wake of the McMonagle
OL,14,Fscandal.
OL,16,FMcMonagle, from Limewood Street in
OL,17,FLondonderry, was jailed last year
OL,18,Fafter being found guilty of a series
OL,19,Fof offences, including attempting to
OL,20,Fincite a child to engage in sexual
OL,21,Factivity.
