OL,3,CMcMonagle employment may have
OL,4,C'resulted in misuse of public money',
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FThe review found that he had been
OL,8,Femployed by Sinn Fein MP Orfhlaith
OL,9,FBegley from January 2019 until May
OL,10,F2020.
OL,12,FHe began full-time employment with Ms
OL,13,FO'Neill as a press/research adviser in
OL,14,FMarch 2020 and worked for her until
OL,15,Fthe end of May of that year.
OL,17,FIt said at an "unspecified date" in
OL,18,FMarch 2020 he also began employment
OL,19,Fwith Sinn Fein as a press officer on a
OL,20,Fpart-time basis.
