OL,7,FHe began his employment with party MLA
OL,8,FJemma Dolan in June 2020, for whom he
OL,9,Fworked until July 2022.
OL,11,FIn a letter to MLAs, Ms Hogg said: "A
OL,12,Fkey finding of the review is that it
OL,13,Fis likely that ... Mr Michael
OL,14,FMcMonagle, misrepresented details of
OL,15,Fhis employments to his employers
OL,16,Fduring a three-month period from March
OL,17,F2020 to May 2020."
