OL,3,CMcMonagle employment may have
OL,4,C'resulted in misuse of public money',
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FShe went on to say the "likely
OL,8,Fmisrepresentation of his employments
OL,9,Fby Mr McMonagle may have resulted in a
OL,10,Fmisuse of public money" and said the
OL,11,FPSNI had been informed.
OL,13,FMs Hogg added she had advised those
OL,14,FMLAs who employed McMonagle and also
OL,15,FSinn Fein to "consider any further
OL,16,Fsteps that they should take in their
OL,17,Frole as employers".
OL,19,FThe review was carried out by Jonathan
OL,20,FMcMillen, the Assembly's head of legal
OL,21,Fservices.
