OL,4,C'resulted in misuse of public money',
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FHowever, it said Ms O'Neill, now
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister, "is
OL,9,Funlikely to have been aware of all the
OL,10,Femployment contracts to which Mr
OL,11,FMcMonagle was subject at that time,
OL,12,Fand is unlikely have become aware of
OL,13,Fthose contracts during his employment
OL,14,Fwith her".
OL,16,FThe review said the "most serious
OL,17,Fissue to emerge" was that McMonagle
OL,18,Fhad taken up full-time employment with
OL,19,FMs O'Neill in March 2020 when at the
OL,20,Fsame time he was employed by Ms Begley.
