OL,3,CMcMonagle employment may have
OL,4,C'resulted in misuse of public money',
OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FIt said: "If Sinn Fein did provide
OL,8,Fcentralised recruitment facilities to
OL,9,Fmembers of the party, as seems likely,
OL,10,Fit is odd that this was not picked up
OL,11,Funtil October 2024, particularly when
OL,12,FMr McMonagle was at the same time
OL,13,Fworking part-time for the party.
OL,15,F"The result was that Mr McMonagle was
OL,16,Ffor a three-month period entitled to
OL,17,Ftwo full-time salaries from two
OL,18,Fdifferent sources, both drawing on
OL,19,Fpublic funds."
