OL,5,Creview finds
OL,7,FThe review said that for part of the
OL,8,Fperiod it was investigating, public
OL,9,Fhealth measures introduced because of
OL,10,Fthe Covid pandemic were in place
OL,11,F"which affected the way all Members'
OL,12,Femployees carried out their work".
OL,14,FThe review recommended employees
OL,15,Fengaged in party activity should keep
OL,16,Frecords of that activity and the
OL,17,Femploying member should keep a record
OL,18,Fof the hours involved and that MLAs
OL,19,Fshould provide details of employees
OL,20,Fwho hold other employment remunerated
OL,21,Ffrom public money.
